thread.title: Leadership tour inspires Marinette Middle School students
thread.title_full: Leadership tour inspires Marinette Middle School students

author: SUBMITTED
title: Leadership tour inspires Marinette Middle School students
text:
MARINETTE — The University of Wisconsin - Marinette recently served as the venue for the Fall Wisconsin Association of School Councils (WASC) Leadership Tour, with Marinette Middle School Student Council taking the lead as event hosts.
Nearly 300 students from across the region attended the event, which focused on fostering leadership skills and building connections among young leaders.
